{
  "stem": "26447.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And I tell him that's-- and that's what the guys, they have a pistol.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "Maybe come with us together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "We will-- we will try what is-- anyway, we will be killed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "The time in the house I cannot explain to you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "It's not enough words what the people was feeling.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "It's crying.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "It's who cry, who-- who-- who, no-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Terrible feeling.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] When they brought all the people, it's become maybe 2 o'clock day time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They make no corridor from the house, a corridor from both sides, policemen and Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they catch the people and bring them to the door, go out, and they beat them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The time in the house was-- everybody want to live maybe 5 minutes more, 10 minutes more, until the one truck will go and come back, or it will-- or they will come with the other truck.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They take everybody and they put them in with-- with the sticks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They beat us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they put us in the truck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Oh, I didn't say one thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When I told the father, father will go-- come with me and we'll go together.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He say, my son, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I don't-- [PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] I don't want to see your-- you will killed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I want to see what I will-- well, you will see that I've been killed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I decided I will go first.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the father left the house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[SOB] [PAUSES FOR 13 SECONDS] They put in the trucks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we-- we sit in the trucks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The foot must be straight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And to each other straight we sit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And on the feet, they put other people-- they fill up the truck.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But you cannot get up because somebody sit on your feet.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
